Package: flyer
Title: Example geospatial data for cartography
Version: 0.0.1.00
Authors@R: 
    person("Reed", "Benkendorf", , "reedbenkendorf2021@u.northwestern.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: I often find that I need new geospatial data for playing around with cartographic tricks. A normal challenge for me is plotting points and linestrings on large geographic expanses. Here I digitize the locations from The Log from the Sea of Cortez, Ed Ricketts and John Steinbecks legendary collection trip. 
